posting_body: ['**Coming in September!', '**', 'One of the NEWEST apartment homes in Palo Alto and NOW FEATURING UPSCALE, MODERN, REMODELED INTERIORS with high ceilings!', 'Our amazing remodels include brand new wood flooring throughout and *tile flooring in kitchen and bath (*Select homes).', ' Kitchen with brand new ACRYLIC European cabinetry, Quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances including over-the-range microwave.', ' Our sophisticated blend of award-winning architecture, wonderful interiors and convenient location in vibrant Palo Alto make Montage a true gem.', 'Our outstanding collection of one and two bedroom apartment homes is situated around a beautifully landscaped courtyard.', 'Comfort and style abound.', 'CALL NOW!', 'show contact info', 'Washer and dryer inside EVERY home', 'Air conditioner', 'REMODELED interiors!', 'New wood flooring throughout', '*Tile flooring in kitchen and bath', 'Kitchen features brand new cabinets', 'Quartz kitchen countertops', 'Stainless steel appliances including over-the-range microwave', 'Dishwasher/disposal', "9-10' Ceilings", 'Oversized double-paned windows', 'Walk-in closet', '*Private patio/balcony', 'FREE bicycle storage', 'Extra storage available', 'Private garages available', 'Covered parking', 'Palo Alto School Districts (Juana Briones Elementary, Terman Middle School, Gunn High School)', 'Close to California Ave and Page Mill', 'Near shopping, dining and Stanford', 'Easy access to freeways 101 and 280', 'No pets', '(Photos may not be of actual unit)', '*Select homes', '**Rate applies to specific units and new move-ins signing a 12 month lease', 'Call for your tour:', 'show contact info']
